35:04.811 --> 35:11.735
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:34.466 --> 35:38.470
‐ All right, Justin.
Every chop and slash is deep.

35:38.470 --> 35:40.639
Overall, sir, it will KEAL.

35:40.639 --> 35:42.766
‐ Thank you.
‐ All right, Nic.

35:42.766 --> 35:44.392
It's your turn.
Ready to have fun?

35:44.392 --> 35:45.477
‐ Let's do this.

35:45.477 --> 35:47.646
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:47.646 --> 35:50.482
Justin's blade
annihilated that dummy.

35:50.482 --> 35:51.983
<i>I'm not really nervous</i>
<i>about what</i>

35:51.983 --> 35:53.318
<i>the ballistics dummy's</i>
<i>going to do to my blade.</i>

35:53.318 --> 35:56.488
I'm just hoping I turn out
as good as Justin did.

35:56.488 --> 36:03.286
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:24.349 --> 36:27.018
‐ All right, Nic.
Upon impact,

36:27.018 --> 36:29.729
