into this foot soldier.

39:19.107 --> 39:21.651
Over all, sir,
your weapons‐‐it will cut.

39:21.651 --> 39:23.361
‐ Good.

39:23.361 --> 39:25.363
‐ All right, Nic,
your turn, sir. You ready?

39:25.363 --> 39:26.990
‐ Play some good music.

39:26.990 --> 39:33.872
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:50.263 --> 39:51.639
‐ All right, Nic.

39:51.639 --> 39:54.559
No glinting or rolls
through your edges.

39:54.559 --> 39:56.519
Sharp with every cut
that went through.

39:56.519 --> 39:58.688
It will cut.
‐ Thank you.

39:58.688 --> 40:00.064
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:00.064 --> 40:01.900
‐ All right, bladesmiths.

40:01.900 --> 40:05.445
You guys have brought in some
high quality, competitive,

40:05.445 --> 40:07.906
and nicely matched
Frankish throwing axes.

40:07.906 --> 40:10.033
